        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "What can we do to solve these problems?",
        "bbox": [
          0.08368200836820083,
          0.0737448559670782,
          0.42305904230590424,
          0.09020576131687243
        ],
        "order": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2884_1",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "If we eat more vegetables and less meat, we willeasily get more food. Land that is used to grow crops can feed five times more people than land where animals are kept.",
        "bbox": [
          0.05764760576476058,
          0.09481481481481481,
