          0.1336625514403292
        ],
        "order": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2884_2",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The world population will not rise so quickly if people use modern methods of birth control.",
        "bbox": [
          0.07345420734542074,
          0.13695473251028806,
          0.8470478847047884,
          0.15539094650205762
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2884_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Finally, if we educate people to think about the problems, we shall have a beter and cleaner living place n the future.",
